Swash Who - information skill
------------------------------------------------------------
The swho comand will list all active Swashbucklers on
Darkwind, along with a status report for each.  The status
is noted by one or more letters:

D - dead
E - wiz+ editing a file
F - fighting
I - input mode (reading, writing, listing 'who', etc.)
M - muffed
[Idle] - idle

Swashbucklers can change the guild title displayed under
swho by using the stitle command.

